> **Discord Gamecord is a powerful module that allows you to play games within Discord :)**

## **‚öôÔ∏è Installation** 
```
npm i discord-gamecord
```

## **‚ú® Features**

- Super simple and easy to use.
- Beginner friendly.
- Easy to Implement.
- Supports Slash Commands.


## **üìö Usage**
```js
const { Snake } = require('discord-gamecord')

new Snake({
  message: message,
  slash_command: false,
  embed: {
    title: 'Snake Game',
    color: '#5865F2',
    overTitle: 'Game Over',
  },
  snake: { head: 'üü¢', body: 'üü©', tail: 'üü¢' },
  emojis: {
    board: '‚¨õ', 
    food: 'üçé',
    up: '‚¨ÜÔ∏è', 
    right: '‚û°Ô∏è',
    down: '‚¨áÔ∏è',
    left: '‚¨ÖÔ∏è',
  },
}).startGame()
```


## **‚úèÔ∏è Example**
### **Looking for Examples? click here:** [**Examples!**](https://discord-gamecord.js.org/docs/gamecord/master/general/welcome)

```js
const Discord = require('discord.js');
const client = new Discord.Client();
const { Snake } = require('discord-gamecord');


client.on('messageCreate', async (message) => {
  if(message.content === '!snake') {
    new Snake({
      message: message,
      slash_command: false,
      embed: {
        title: 'Snake Game',
        color: '#5865F2',
        overTitle: 'Game Over',
      },
      snake: { head: 'üü¢', body: 'üü©', tail: 'üü¢' },
      emojis: {
        board: '‚¨õ',
        food: 'üçé',
        up: '‚¨ÜÔ∏è', 
        down: '‚¨áÔ∏è',
        right: '‚û°Ô∏è',
        left: '‚¨ÖÔ∏è',
      }
    }).startGame();
  }
});

client.login('YOUR_COOL_DISCORD_BOT_TOKEN');
```

